  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：VinciCoder</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"344\" data-imgfileid=\"100016729\" data-ratio=\"0.30277777777777776\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1136\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bb3d8617&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzLs7rPcAqvZlw0ibmZWP4wicFvxC1teAHouFfB4t7ibkpT1ZD1yZHGODut7EomuI83q8z2Durfn8ETA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★VinciCoder 是一个多模态代码生成项目，旨在通过粗到细的视觉强化学习统一多模态代码生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目提供了丰富的数据集和训练脚本，支持从图表到代码、网页到HTML、图像到SVG、图像到LaTeX等多种任务的代码生成。项目基于 ms-swift 和 EasyR1 框架进行训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vincicoder\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vincicoder</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Depth-Anything-3</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39351851851851855\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1138\" data-height=\"448\" data-imgfileid=\"100016731\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d91a84e4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzLs7rPcAqvZlw0ibmZWP4wiczpYmp3ayvHzgu5o27RdUdUN3XEH8HfqE6MiaPoOgHZkkbXxcg8jctXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Depth Anything 3 (DA3) 是一个能够从任意视觉输入中预测空间一致几何的模型，无论是否已知相机位姿。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">DA3 通过使用单一的 Transformer 作为骨干网络和深度射线表示，简化了模型架构。该模型在单目深度估计、多视图深度估计和位姿估计方面显著优于其前代版本 DA2 和 VGGT。所有模型均在公共学术数据集上进行训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/depth-anything-3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/depth-anything-3</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：RouterLens</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.387037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1142\" data-height=\"442\" data-imgfileid=\"100016730\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e357330&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzLs7rPcAqvZlw0ibmZWP4wicugrwkGMVTPksbCF8mc681RrtlXiaqdicypibBt54aBl6HwyB0p7miafNmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★RouterLens 是一个轻量级工具，旨在有效识别 Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) 大型语言模型中的专家。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">这些专家在不同领域和任务中表现出专长，但通常受到负载平衡约束的限制。RouterLens 通过识别和利用上下文忠实专家，提出了一种参数高效的调优方法——上下文忠实专家微调（CEFT），在显著减少可训练参数数量的同时，实现了与全量微调相当的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/routerlens\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/routerlens</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：EverMemOS</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25277777777777777\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1138\" data-height=\"288\" data-imgfileid=\"100016728\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c79431c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzLs7rPcAqvZlw0ibmZWP4wicD0YEslKIsib0I1gysNAjW4cBw10icruQVdAS7sVrPe7wuRe06WDSgBrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★EverMemOS 是一个前瞻性的智能系统，不仅仅是一个“回顾”数据库。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它使得人工智能不仅能够“记住”发生过的事情，还能“理解”这些记忆背后的意义，并利用它们来指导当前的行动和决策。在 EverMemOS 的演示工具中，可以看到它如何从历史中提取重要信息，并在对话中记住用户的偏好、习惯和历史，就像一个真正了解你的朋友。在 LoCoMo 基准测试中，基于 EverMemOS 的方法实现了 92.3% 的推理准确率，优于我们评估中的可比方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/evermemos\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/evermemos</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：WithAnyone</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5111111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1138\" data-height=\"582\" data-imgfileid=\"100016732\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6b204376&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzLs7rPcAqvZlw0ibmZWP4wicqfZY7olbIb5VS7TqF39j74pgK8Aiaxmq7icfummDZG7HNOyVzicfXB2yw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★WithAnyone 是一个能够生成高质量、可控且身份一致的图像的项目。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它旨在解决面部生成中的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">“复制粘贴”伪影问题</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，通过提供更好的表情、发型、配饰和姿势的可控性，打破了相似性与复制粘贴之间的权衡。此外，WithAnyone 支持多身份生成，可以在单张图像中生成多个给定身份，使所有生成的面孔在一张合影中和谐地融合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/withanyone\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/withanyone</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Pelican1.0-VL</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5416666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1138\" data-height=\"616\" data-imgfileid=\"100016733\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0f950afd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzLs7rPcAqvZlw0ibmZWP4wicJ6ZEnu6PWPRpViabfp7e9liaqscL0QdVliazQSVd9xhh3K9dxSozHtuDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Pelican-VL 1.0 是一款开源的多模态脑模型，参数规模从7B到72B不等。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">深度整合数据能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">智能自适应学习机制</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，能够处理视觉和文本输入，进行物体识别、物理推理、空间关系理解和功能预测。其应用领域包括机器人任务中的物体抓取、导航和协作操作，展示了强大的跨任务泛化能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/pelican1-0-vl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/pelican1-0-vl</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总了今日最新的六个开源 AI 项目，涵盖多模态代码生成、深度估计、MoE 模型专家识别、智能体记忆系统、高质量图像生成和多模态脑模型等前沿技术。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总了今日最新的六个开源 AI 项目，涵盖多模态代码生成、深度估计、MoE 模型专家识别、智能体记忆系统、高质量图像生成和多模态脑模型等前沿技术。",
  "summary": "这篇文章是《机器之心 SOTA 模型》栏目发布的“今日开源”系列，聚焦于 2025 年 11 月 17 日的最新 AI 开源项目。文章精选并简要介绍了六个前沿项目，包括：中科院与美团联合开源的 VinciCoder（通过视觉强化学习统一多模态代码生成），Depth-Anything-3（预测空间一致几何模型），RouterLens（MoE 大模型专家识别及高效微调），EverMemOS（具备理解和决策能力的智能体记忆系统），WithAnyone（高质量、身份一致的图像生成），以及 Pelican1.0-VL（多模态脑模型）。每个项目都提供了核心功能概述和 SOTA 模型平台的收藏链接，旨在帮助技术从业者快速了解和获取最新的 AI 技术进展和开源资源。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "VinciCoder 通过视觉强化学习统一多模态代码生成，解决视觉保真度痛点。",
      "explanation": "该项目能够从图表、网页、图像等多种视觉输入生成代码，有效提升了多模态代码生成的视觉保真度和统一性，对于提升开发效率具有重要意义。"
